OL,3,CJames Bulger's mother: I needed to see
OL,4,Cthe faces of my son's killers
OL,6,FAs Brianna Ghey's teenage murderers
OL,7,Fare set to be identified at their
OL,8,Fsentencing hearing on Friday, and
OL,9,Ftheir faces revealed publicly for the
OL,10,Ffirst time, ITV News' Evening News
OL,11,FPresenter Mary Nightingale sat down
OL,12,Fwith the mother of James Bulger,
OL,13,FDenise Fergus, who insisted Brianna's
OL,14,Ffamily deserve to know the identity of
OL,15,Fher killers.
OL,17,FIt's the dignity that strikes you
OL,18,Fimmediately. The measured calm of a
OL,19,Fwoman who has been through so much `
OL,20,Fhas suffered such loss.
