OL,3,CJames Bulger's mother: I needed to see
OL,4,Cthe faces of my son's killers
OL,6,FDenise Fergus faces the world with the
OL,7,Fimplacable determination of a seasoned
OL,8,Fcampaigner.
OL,10,FNothing and nobody diverts her from
OL,11,Fher purpose ` that of seeking justice
OL,12,Ffor the child victims of murder, and
OL,13,Ftheir families.
OL,15,FDenise's son died 31 years ago `
OL,16,Fabducted tortured and killed by two 10-
OL,17,Fyear-old boys.
