OL,3,CJames Bulger's mother: I needed to see
OL,4,Cthe faces of my son's killers
OL,6,FAnyone old enough to remember the case
OL,7,Fwill not have forgotten the
OL,8,Fdesperation of the young mother,
OL,9,Fappealing for the return of her
OL,10,Fprecious boy.
OL,12,FPhotos of Denise's anguished face,
OL,13,Falongside that of her smiling blond
OL,14,Fhaired toddler, filled the front pages
OL,15,Ffor months.
OL,17,FOnce the killers, Robert Thompson and
OL,18,FJohn Venables, were convicted, we
OL,19,Fbecame horribly familiar with their
OL,20,Ffaces and names, too.
