OL,3,CJames Bulger's mother: I needed to see
OL,4,Cthe faces of my son's killers
OL,6,FThe judge took the unusual decision to
OL,7,Fidentify the pair even though they
OL,8,Fwere under 18. Their childish faces
OL,9,Fshocked the nation then ` and still do.
OL,11,FThree decades later, I'm in Liverpool
OL,12,Fto get Denise's views on another
OL,13,Ftragic case of children killing a
OL,14,Fchild, this time, 16-year-old .
OL,16,FWhen Brianna's teenage murderers are
OL,17,Fsentenced tomorrow, they too will be
OL,18,Fidentified, their faces revealed
OL,19,Fpublicly for the first time.
